The shift in search from chaotic results to verified answers has made it more important than ever to continually optimize your search strategies. 

What are consumers searching for today that they weren’t searching for a month ago? What experience do they expect? 

Every brand will need a hero — an expert who understands the evolving customer journey, how to provide brand-verified answers, and maximize customer engagement.

To learn more visit: hitchhikers.yext.com
